<span class="Apple-style-span">
</span>
<p>
<a href="http://www.seas.harvard.edu/administration/deans-office/biography" class="internal-link" title="Biography"><strong>Cherry A. Murray</strong></a><br>Dean, Harvard School of Engineering and Applied Sciences<br>ï»¿John A. and Elizabeth S. Armstrong Professor of Engineering and Applied Sciences<br>Professor of Physics</p>
